ZH: 明天要参加重要的考试。
EN: I have an important exam tomorrow.

ZH: 考试之前要好好复习。
EN: You need to study well before the exam.

ZH: 我们要在考试中取得好成绩。
EN: We need to get good grades in the exam.

ZH: 考试结束后，我们都松了口气。
EN: We all breathed a sigh of relief after the exam was over.

ZH: 考试的时候不要作弊。
EN: Don't cheat during the exam.

ZH: 考试成绩会决定我们的未来。
EN: Exam results will determine our future.

ZH: 考试的题目很难吗？
EN: Are the exam questions difficult?

ZH: 考试的时间快到了。
EN: The exam is coming soon.

ZH: 我们需要小心答题，不能马虎。
EN: We need to be careful in answering the questions and not be careless.

ZH: 我希望这次考试能有好的表现。
EN: I hope to perform well in this exam.

ZH: 考试结果出来了吗？
EN: Have the exam results been released?

ZH: 我一直在为考试做准备。
EN: I have been preparing for the exam all along.

ZH: 可以问老师关于考试的问题。
EN: You can ask the teacher questions about the exam.

ZH: 考试完后我们可以一起庆祝。
EN: We can celebrate together after the exam.

ZH: 你准备好这次考试了吗？
EN: Are you ready for this exam?

ZH: 我要好好发挥在考试中。
EN: I will do my best in the exam.

ZH: 考试不只是为了分数，更要学到东西。
EN: Exams are not just for scores, but also for learning.

ZH: 我的考试成绩不像我预期的那样好。
EN: My exam results are not as good as I expected.

ZH: 每次考试都是一个挑战。
EN: Every exam is a challenge.

ZH: 去考试之前要准备好文具。
EN: Be sure to prepare your stationery before the exam.
